text: Supreme Sundar is an Action Choreographer in Indian Film Industry who have won the National Film Award for Best Stunt Choreography for the movie Ayyappanum Koshiyum. He is also known for his Action Choreography in the movie 'Animal, which was nominated for Filmfare Awards for Best Action Choreography, Thunivu, Bheeshma Parvam, Kannur Squad, Thallumaala etc. ==Filmography== He has worked as Action Choreographer in over 30 movies. * Animal (2023 Indian film) * Ayyappanum Koshiyum * Bheeshma Parvam * Thunivu * Kannur Squad * Thallumaala * Kanguva * Vidaamyurachi == Awards == * Won National Film Award for Best Stunt Choreography, 2020. * Nomination for Best Action Choreography in Filmfare Awards, 2024. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Living people Category:Indian action choreographers
title: Supreme Sundar
